	species(canonicalName: "Felis catus") {
		wholeGenomes(page: 1, pageSize: 5, filters: [{ filter: ASSEMBLY_LEVEL, action: INCLUDE, value: "Contig"}]) {
			total
			records {
				sequenceId
				dnaExtractId
				datasetName
				recordId
				latitude
				longitude
				accession
				materialSampleId
				name
				quality
				releaseType
				representation
				versionStatus
				estimatedSize
				excludedFromRefseq
				assemblyType
				genomeSize
				dataType
				sequencedBy
				assembledBy
				annotatedBy
				depositedBy
			}
		}
	}
}
"}

{"query":"{
  search(filters: [
		{ filter: DATA_TYPE, action: INCLUDE, value: "Taxon" },
		{ filter: DATA_TYPE, action: INCLUDE, value: "Genome" },
	]) {
		fullText (query: "corroboree", perPage: 20, page: 0) {
			total
			records {
				... on TaxonItem {
					type
					status
					score
					canonicalName
					commonNames
					subspecies
					synonyms
					classification {
						kingdom
						phylum
						class
						order
						family
						genus
					}
					dataSummary {
						assemblies
						referenceGenomes
						wholeGenomes
						partialGenomes
						barcodes
					}
				}
				... on GenomeItem {
					type
					status
					score
					canonicalName
					accession
					genomeRep
					dataSource
					level
					referenceGenome
					releaseDate
				}
				... on LocusItem {
					type
					status
					score
					canonicalName
					accession
					locusType
					dataSource
					voucherStatus
					eventDate
					eventLocation
				}
				... on SpecimenItem {
					type
					status
					score
					canonicalName
					accession
					dataSource
					institutionCode
					collectionCode
					recordedBy
					identifiedBy
					eventDate
					eventLocation
				}
			}
		}
  }
}"}
